OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,FThe authority that holds Jersey's
OL,7,FPolice force to account has called for
OL,8,Fan "urgent" review of the force's
OL,9,Fbudget, saying insufficient funding
OL,10,Fmeans public policing could be
OL,11,F"seriously compromised".
OL,13,FThe Jersey Police Authority's chair,
OL,14,FSimon Harman, told the Jersey Evening
OL,15,FPost that "the current budget
OL,16,Fproposals, while fiscally restrained,
OL,17,Fdo not provide the flexibility or
OL,18,Fgrowth necessary to sustain that
OL,19,Fstandard (of policing)".
