OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,FHe added he was "concerned" that a
OL,7,F"reduction in resourcing" would result
OL,8,Ffrom constrained budgets, which
OL,9,F"carries significant operational,
OL,10,Freputational, and social risks".
OL,12,FThe Government's proposed Budget for
OL,13,F2026 has set aside around #31 million,
OL,14,Fmore money than this year, to fund the
OL,15,Fforce.
OL,17,FThe island's Chief of Police says
OL,18,Fdespite any financial challenges, he
OL,19,Fremains "absolutely confident that we
OL,20,Fwill maintain safety for islanders".
