OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,FRobin Smith told ITV News that whilst
OL,7,Fthis year has seen an additional
OL,8,Fstrain on police resources - with a
OL,9,F27% increase in reported crimes
OL,10,Finvolving violence against women and
OL,11,Fgirls - they have worked to
OL,12,F"strenuously show how we are both
OL,13,Feffective and efficient".
OL,15,F"There isn't a Police Chief in the
OL,16,Fworld who's not going to say he or she
OL,17,Fwould like more resources", he says,
OL,18,F"but we see the island has a
OL,19,Fchallenging financial landscape".
