OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,F"We're always looking to provide
OL,7,Fgreater and greater efficiencies", he
OL,8,Fexplains, "so yes, we are looking to
OL,9,Fmove different resources into
OL,10,Fdifferent places - but we are trying
OL,11,Fto maintain the safety of the island".
OL,13,FIn order to tackle the rise in crimes
OL,14,Fagainst women and girls, the force
OL,15,Fplans to "move resources to support
OL,16,Four public protection teams and
OL,17,Fcriminal investigation department -
OL,18,Fbecause that's the obvious and natural
OL,19,Fthing to do".
