OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,FKate Wright, Chair of the Violence
OL,7,FAgainst Women and Girls (VAWG)
OL,8,FTaskforce, feels "the response from
OL,9,Fthe police to the well-documented and
OL,10,Fsignificant rise in demand on their
OL,11,Fservices has been really positive"
OL,12,Fwhen it comes to dealing with these
OL,13,Ftypes of crimes.
OL,15,F"We have noticed a real transformation
OL,16,Fin terms of the support", she adds,
OL,17,F"and all credit to the police for
OL,18,Frising to that challenge".
