OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,FHowever, Kate says that whilst all
OL,7,Fparties involved recognise that
OL,8,Fresources are finite and the island's
OL,9,Fcurrent financial landscape is
OL,10,Fchallenging, "when the Government is
OL,11,Flooking at funding, it's really
OL,12,Fimportant they take a holistic view".
OL,14,F"(Tackling) violence against women and
OL,15,Fgirls is, quite rightly, a strategic
OL,16,Fpriority", she explains, "and if we
OL,17,Fwant to do that properly without
OL,18,Fdamaging the quality of support to
OL,19,Fsurvivors and trust, then it's
OL,20,Fimportant that investment continues".
