OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,FMembers of the community policing team
OL,7,Fhave already been redeployed to the
OL,8,Fpublic protection teams and criminal
OL,9,Finvestigation departments - something
OL,10,Fthe island's Chairman of the Committee
OL,11,Fof the Chef de Police says adds to the
OL,12,Fexisting strain on the Honourary
OL,13,FPolice force - which is down around
OL,14,F100 officers.
OL,16,F"Come weekends, (the community police)
OL,17,Fare suffering from officers out in the
OL,18,Fevening", Joao Camara explains, "if
OL,19,Fthere is more than one incident, then
OL,20,Fthey are struggling".
