OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,FDespite these challenges, Joao agrees
OL,7,Fthe safety of islanders "is not in
OL,8,Fdoubt".
OL,10,FPolice Chief Smith says 10 new
OL,11,Fofficers have already been recruited
OL,12,Fto the States of Jersey Police - with
OL,13,Fa price tag of approximately #1
OL,14,Fmillion - to start work in the New
OL,15,FYear.
