OL,3,CJersey's Chief of Police confident
OL,4,Cdespite funding concerns
OL,6,FHe also describes 2026 as a
OL,7,F"transitional year", during which the
OL,8,Fforce will "work with the police
OL,9,Fauthority and government to work out
OL,10,Fin 2026 what additional funding we
OL,11,Fneed moving into 2027".
OL,13,FHowever, he declined to provide a
OL,14,Fballpark figure - saying they will
OL,15,F"carefully go through the data so we
OL,16,Fcan properly assess what the increase
OL,17,Fin demand is - not just in policing,
OL,18,Fbut across the whole judicial system".
